high_descs: Turn and go to the sink on the right.
Pick up the spray bottle by the sink.
Go to the cabinets under the sink on the right.
Put the spray bottle in the cabinets under the sink.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle on the toilet.
Turn around and go to the cabinets under the sink on the right.
Put the spray bottle in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the spray bottles to the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the toilet
Pick up a bottle from the counter
Move to the cabinet to the second from the right against the wall
Put the bottle in the cabinet
Move to the toilet behind you
Pick up a bottle from the toilet
Move to the cabinet to the second from the right against the wall
Put the bottle in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles in a cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the sink in front of you.
Pick up the blue spray bottle.
Back up a step.
Open the left cabinet door under the sink and put the spray bottle down there and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the blue spray bottle.
Go back to where you put the first spray bottle.
Put the spray bottle next to the other one and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the sink against the wall.
Pick up a spray bottle from the counter.
Move back a few steps from the sink.
Open the  cabinet to the left under the sink ahead of you and place the bottle inside and close it.
Turn around to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle on the toilet.
Turn around to the sink behind you.
Open the  cabinet to the left under the sink ahead of you and place the bottle inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the cabinet under the sink against the wall.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the wall, after that turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the blue spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet, then turn around to face the sink.
Open the second cabinet door from the right and place the spray bottle inside on the front right edge.
Turn around and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and take a step forward.
Open the second cabinet door from the right and place the spray bottle inside to the left of the spray bottle that is already in there.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the front of the sink on the right side of the counter ahead.
Pick up the blue spray bottle that's to the right of the faucet.
Face the cabinets below the sink on the right side.
Open the cabinet on the left side below the right sink, place the blue spray bottle in the cabinet, and close the door.
Turn around and face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the blue spray bottle from the back of the toilet in between the two candles.
Turn around and face the cabinets below the right side sink.
Open the door on the left side, place the blue spray bottle to the left of the first spray bottle, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the cabinet below the sink on the right side.
